:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:09:11.000Z","msg":"因為讀is land ，會變左廣東話既伊斯蘭...<br />\n咁全世界為左就廣東話，就收埋個s既音。"},{"pid":"6c2f00c0fb8653ed567ab84a0b854936c8ebbbc6","tid":1010763,"uid":108740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:20:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/viwvd-ZIr6s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fviwvd-ZIr6s&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=3b0ae3f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/viwvd-ZIr6s</a>"},{"pid":"178cac348175ade590522ffb7f3b71149b0054cb","tid":1010763,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:21:30.000Z","msg":"中文點解唔直譯是地"},{"pid":"dea25eaab844d8d26e75f5379a438cbceac358cc","tid":1010763,"uid":68457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8413cb6ecce5abbac2f718fbc70d93353248b4b7","tid":1010763,"uid":39496,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T08:34:07.000Z","msg":"全世界讀開咁讀就係咁讀<br />\n<br />\n有啲野唔需要解釋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:22:37.000Z","msg":"是，全世界讀嘢唔洗樓主教"},{"pid":"f3e02181b38fd7cb45acc7b8213eb3b537adceea","tid":1010763,"uid":69779,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T09:47:16.000Z","msg":"說來話長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實本身「island」係來自上古英語嘅「igland」<br />\n而後來有人將佢同法文同一個意思嘅「&icirc;le」混淆咗，以為係&icirc;le + land<br />\n而「&icirc;le」係來自拉丁文「insula」，而拉丁文演變成現代法文嘅過程入面，音節尾嘅「s」如果下一個音節嘅頭一個音係consonant嘅話就會消失<br />\n其他例子包括forest -&gt; 現代法文 for&ecirc;t，castel -&gt; 現代法文 ch&acirc;teau 等等<br />\n所以當時&icirc;le仍然係串做「isle」<br />\n所以啲人就將「isle」同「land」擺埋一齊，變咗做「island」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a367b4eac4e7a1574e37858f2873e788fe74